{"tid":2337262,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黎智英今高院申保釋  指定法官李運騰批准保釋","createTime":"2020-12-23T07:23:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T08:39:53.000Z","uid":3799,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"adca27a99cc0ed0c7f20c81593192b478499d508","tid":2337262,"uid":3799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:23:31.000Z","msg":"壹傳媒主席黎智英早前被控詐騙，被拒保釋還押候訊，其後突遭加控一項《港區國安法》下「勾結外國或境外勢力危害國家安全罪」，同樣不獲保釋，案件均押後至明年4月16再訊，他其後就兩案向高等法院申請保釋，今由國安法「指定法官」李運騰處理，法官聽罷雙方陳詞後，批准黎智英保釋。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUPqbQN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUPqbQN.png&h=decef5b8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5e4415406cbfcdf9adecd982eeef06d0002d92b","tid":2337262,"uid":245203,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"完全冇諗過會咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c61731d8734beff5d17ec6749293ae71c09eb20","tid":2337262,"uid":107681,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b5e4415406cbfcdf9adecd982eeef06d0002d92b","tid":2337262,"uid":245203,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:24:44.000Z","msg":"完全冇諗過會咁<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:26:02.000Z","msg":"有險可守？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385917f3269d5db9884f462dea429f4a896d887a","tid":2337262,"uid":76609,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"懷疑李運騰受外國勢力恐嚇"},{"pid":"e2c667e3f472a8631bb331df